                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "262bfdad8e4f",
                  "text": "BMWCCA PSR presents our March 8th, 2026 Car Control Clinic at Pacific Raceways in Kent, Washington\nCost: $150 Includes Lunch. Note: MSR has added an additional $2 fee per registration unless you are a Hagerty Drivers Club member.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "1cae9b5f305b",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "30a9c804e4a3",
                  "text": "Registration will be closed when this class reaches capacity or 7 days prior to the event, whichever occurs first.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "b52afcfd90df",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "4d348e48062e",
                  "text": "Car Control Clinics are a fun way to learn what the vehicle you drive every day is truly capable of doing in emergency and high stress situations. Exercises include Emergency Braking, Accident Avoidance, Wet Skipad, Slalom and a higher speed handling oval. At lunch you will be allowed to take your car onto the track for a few parade laps led by instructors.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "f8662afc9c75",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "37b8f35defe4",
                  "text": "There will be a mandatory online ground school prior to the CCC to learn car control theory and terminology.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "681f71de99e7",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "dd052d10ea5f",
                  "text": "HOT laps . After you complete all of the exercises for the day you have the opportunity to borrow a helmet for a few fast laps around the track in an instructor's car with the instructor driving.",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "_type": "block",
              "_key": "cfeaa37025e2",
              "style": "normal",
              "markDefs": [],
              "children": [
                {
                  "_type": "span",
                  "_key": "42a575fc6803",
                  "text": "Car Control Clinic and HPDE sessions run simultaneously. It is not possible to attend both CCC and HPDE on the same day.\nSee https://bmw-club-psr.org/car-control-clinics for more information",
                  "marks": []
                }
              ]
            }
