          "description": "<h3 style=\"color:#aaaaaa; font-style:italic\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">BMWCCA PSR presents our April&nbsp;16th, 2026&nbsp;Car Control Clinic at Pacific Raceways in Kent, Washington</span></h3>\n<p><em>Cost:&nbsp; &nbsp;$150&nbsp;Includes Lunch.</em> Note: MSR has added an additional $2 fee per registration unless you are a Hagerty Drivers Club member.<em>&nbsp;</em></p>\n<p><em>Registration will be closed when this class reaches capacity or 7&nbsp;days prior to the event, whichever occurs first.</em></p>\n<p><strong><em>Car Control Clinics are a fun way to learn what the vehicle you drive every day is truly capable of doing in emergency and high stress situations. &nbsp;Exercises include Emergency Braking, Accident Avoidance, Wet Skipad, Slalom and a higher speed handling oval.&nbsp; At lunch you will be allowed to take your car onto the track for a few parade laps led by instructors.</em></strong></p>\n<p>There will be a mandatory&nbsp;online ground school prior to the CCC to learn car control theory and terminology.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>HOT laps</strong>.<strong><em>&nbsp; After you complete all of the exercises for the day you have the opportunity&nbsp;to borrow a helmet for a few fast laps around the track in an instructor's car with the instructor driving.&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"color:#aaaaaa; font-style:italic\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000\">Car Control Clinic and&nbsp;HPDE&nbsp;sessions run simultaneously. &nbsp;It is not possible to attend both CCC and HPDE on the same day.</span></strong></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color:black\">See</span> <a style=\"color:blue; text-decoration:underline\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://bmw-club-psr.org/car-control-clinics\">https://bmw-club-psr.org/car-control-clinics</a> <span style=\"color:black\">for more information</span></p>\n<h3 style=\"color:#aaaaaa; font-style:italic\">&nbsp;</h3>",
